description: This file defines a Header component for a food ordering web application frontend, implemented with Qwik framework. It manages user login state, navigation links, and logout functionality.

methods.name: Header
methods.description: A Qwik component that renders the header section including brand, navigation, and user action buttons.

methods.name: onLogout
methods.description: A function triggered when the logout button is clicked; it logs out the user and updates the user signal.
